comment.update
Fired within five minutes of a comment or reply being created, deleted, or the comment visibility settings being modified on any photo post or public video post under an owned TikTok account. This applies to both posts published through /business/video/publish/ or /business/photo/publish/ and posts manually published through the TikTok App.

Prerequisite
To ensure that you can receive comment.update events, the TikTok account owner needs to authorize the developer app with the comment.list scope (Read the comments and replies of your in-app content).

