Miscellaneous
Q1: Does IP address affect the reach of a post when I publish the post through /business/video/publish/ or /business/photo/publish/?

A: No, IP address has no impact on these post publishing endpoints:

The /business/video/publish/ and /business/photo/publish/ endpoints have no IP-based restrictions.
Your API call's IP address does not affect post reach. Post reach is determined solely by your TikTok account's region.